  m_text: 'How to Play

    [ Controls ]


    Move: WASD


    Sprint: Hold [Shift]
    to run faster


    Pick Up / Release: Press [F]


    Throw Item: Press [Q]


    Action:
    [Spacebar] Water the trees


    Menu: [ESC] Open Settings


    [ Survival Tips
    ]


    Warning: Don''t let Maple overheat!


    Refresh: Dive into the pond
    to cool down.


    [ Weather System ]


    Sunny: Heat rises faster.


    Cloudy:
    Heat rises slower.


    [ Quick Start ]


    Try it!: Drag the shovel to the
    soil to begin.'
