    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Game Information

    General Details

    Title: Sunny Splash: Forest
    Revival


    Developer: Pedrimtare Team


    Version: 0.1 (Alpha)


    Story

    In
    a world facing extreme drought, the lush green forests have withered away. Join
    "Maple," a brave little duck, on a mission to bring life back to nature. Use
    your water to refresh the dying trees, manage your "Overheat" levels, and restore
    the forest to its former glory. Every drop counts in this refreshing journey!


    Credits
    & Assets

    Art & Environment: Cainos, Violet Theme UI, MiMU STUDIO, devnik,
    Black Hammer, Hippo, LAYERLAB, maanetorn, Pixel Frog


    Contact & Community

    Discord:


    -
    starlight_456


    - janleab


    - jamekungtv


    - _ham_s


    Thank you
    for playing and supporting our green mission!'
